name: 78 Barrie Street
access: Location: 78 Barrie Street is located at the intersection of Barrie and Stuart St.

Main Entrance
78 Barrie Street is not wheelchair accessible.

Elevator
There is no elevator in the building. Floors 2 and 3 are inaccessible.

Washrooms
There are no accessible washrooms. All washrooms are single-user.
